results.name: a(n) = gcd(n,10).
formula: a(n) = 1 + [2|n] + 4*[5|n] + 4*[10|n], where [x|y] = 1 when x divides y, 0 otherwise.
Multiplicative with a(p^e, 10) = gcd(p^e, 10). - _David W. Wilson_, Jun 12 2005
Dirichlet g.f.: zeta(s)*(1 + 1/2^s + 4/5^s + 4/10^s). - _R. J. Mathar_, Apr 04 2011
results.author: _Mitch Harris_
